06.383" end="00:06.545">ing</span> <span begin="00:06.545" end="00:06.681">to</span> <span begin="00:06.681" end="00:06.944">get</span> <span begin="00:06.944" end="00:07.390">this</span> <span begin="00:07.390" end="00:07.847">one</span> <span begin="00:07.847" end="00:08.413">chance</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:06.528" end="00:08.843"><span begin="00:06.528" end="00:06.835">(Six</span> <span begin="00:06.835" end="00:06.908">mi</span><span begin="00:06.908" end="00:07.107">nutes</span> <span begin="00:08.315" end="00:08.579">six</span> <span begin="00:08.579" end="00:08.599">mi</span><span begin="00:08.599" end="00:08.843">nutes)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">六分钟 六分钟</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可是我要把握这唯一的机会</span></p><p begin="00:09.163" end="00:11.317" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:09.163" end="00:09.712">Some</span><span begin="00:09.712" end="00:10.130">thing's</span> <span begin="00:10.130" end="00:10.602">wrong</span> <span begin="00:10.602" end="00:10.728">I</span> <span begin="00:10.728" end="00:10.902">can</span> <span begin="00:10.902" end="00:11.100">feel</span> <span begin="00:11.100" end="00:11.317">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">情况有点儿不对 我能感觉到</span></p><p begin="00:11.451" end="00:15.575" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:11.451" end="00:12.008">Just</span> <span begin="00:12.473" end="00:12.777">a</span> <span begin="00:12.777" end="00:12.895">fee</span><span begin="00:12.895" end="00:13.077">ling</span> <span begin="00:13.077" end="00:13.185">I've</span> <span begin="00:13.185" end="00:13.422">got</span> <span begin="00:14.133" end="00:14.300">like</span> <span begin="00:14.300" end="00:14.501">some</span><span begin="00:14.501" end="00:14.710">thing's</span> <span begin="00:14.710" end="00:14.853">a</span><span begin="00:14.853" end="00:15.018">bout</span> <span begin="00:15.018" end="00:15.203">to</span> <span begin="00:15.203" end="00:15.328">hap</span><span begin="00:15.328" end="00:15.575">pen</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:11.570" end="00:12.937"><span begin="00:11.570" end="00:11.800">(Six</span> <span begin="00:11.800" end="00:11.849">mi</span><span begin="00:11.849" end="00:11.970">nutes</span> <span begin="00:11.971" end="00:12.142">Slim</span> <span begin="00:12.142" end="00:12.260">Sha</span><span begin="00:12.260" end="00:12.379">dy</span> <span begin="00:12.379" end="00:12.521">you're</span> <span begin="00:12.521" end="00:12.937">on)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">六分钟 Slim Shady 该你出场了！</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只是觉得 要出大事了</span></p><p begin="00:16.110" end="00:17.257" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:16.110" end="00:16.157">But</span> <span begin="00:16.157" end="00:16.332">I</span> <span begin="00:16.332" end="00:16.566">don't</span> <span begin="00:16.566" end="00:16.908">know</span> <span begin="00:16.908" end="00:17.257">what</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:16.398" end="00:16.876"><span begin="00:16.398" end="00:16.630">(Six</span> <span begin="00:16.630" end="00:16.707">mi</span><span begin="00:16.707" end="00:16.876">nutes)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">六分钟</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是我不知道会发生什么</span></p><p begin="00:17.670" end="00:20.947" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:17.670" end="00:17.875">If</span> <span begin="00:17.875" end="00:18.037">that</span> <span begin="00:18.037" end="00:18.250">means</span> <span begin="00:18.250" end="00:18.351">what</span> <span begin="00:18.351" end="00:18.601">I</span> <span begin="00:18.601" end="00:18.731">think</span> <span begin="00:18.731" end="00:18.862">it</span> <span begin="00:18.862" end="00:19.125">means</span> <span begin="00:19.316" end="00:19.401">we're</span> <span begin="00:19.401" end="00:19.651">in</span> <span begin="00:19.651" end="00:19.793">trou</span><span begin="00:19.793" end="00:20.005">ble</span> <span begin="00:20.413" end="00:20.623">big</span> <span begin="00:20.623" end="00:20.729">trou</span><span begin="00:20.729" end="00:20.947">ble</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:18.033" end="00:19.390"><span begin="00:18.033" end="00:18.224">(Six</span> <span begin="00:18.224" end="00:18.355">mi</span><span begin="00:18.355" end="00:18.422">nutes,</span> <span begin="00:18.422" end="00:18.641">Slim</span> <span begin="00:18.641" end="00:18.739">Sha</span><span begin="00:18.739" end="00:18.862">dy</span> <span begin="00:18.862" end="00:18.995">you're</span> <span begin="00:18.995" end="00:19.390">on)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">六分钟 Slim Shady 该你出场了！</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若是一切如我所料 我们会遇上麻烦</span></p><p begin="00:21.132" end="00:24.238" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:21.132" end="00:21.179">And</span> <span begin="00:21.179" end="00:21.247">if</span> <span begin="00:21.247" end="00:21.371">he</span> <span begin="00:21.371" end="00:21.444">is</span> <span begin="00:21.444" end="00:21.579">as</span> <span begin="00:21.579" end="00:21.655">ba</span><span begin="00:21.655" end="00:21.806">na</span><span begin="00:21.806" end="00:22.127">nas</span> <span begin="00:22.127" end="00:22.239">as</span> <span begin="00:22.239" end="00:22.336">you</span> <span begin="00:22.336" end="00:22.703">say</span> <span begin="00:22.996" end="00:23.136">I'm</span> <span begin="00:23.136" end="00:23.367">not</span> <span begin="00:23.367" end="00:23.475">ta</span><span begin="00:23.475" end="00:23.632">king</span> <span begin="00:23.632" end="00:23.694">a</span><span begin="00:23.694" end="00:23.780">ny</span> <span begin="00:23.780" end="00:23.983">chan</span><span begin="00:23.983" end="00:24.238">ces</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">若他真像你说的那样疯狂 我绝不会去冒任何险的</span></p><p begin="00:24.469" end="00:25.819" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:24.469" end="00:24.538">You</span> <span begin="00:24.538" end="00:24.614">are</span> <span begin="00:24.614" end="00:24.801">just</span> <span begin="00:24.801" end="00:24.967">what</span> <span begin="00:24.967" end="00:25.205">the</span> <span begin="00:25.205" end="00:25.349">doc</span> <span begin="00:25.531" end="00:25.691">or</span><span begin="00:25.691" end="00:25.819">dered</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你可是Dr. Dre相中的人才！</span></p><p begin="00:25.875" end="00:28.927" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:25.875" end="00:26.090">I'm</span> <span begin="00:26.090" end="00:26.315">be</span><span begin="00:26.315" end="00:26.504">gin</span><span begin="00:26.504" end="00:26.696">nin'</span> <span begin="00:26.696" end="00:26.862">to</span> <span begin="00:26.862" end="00:27.047">feel</span> <span begin="00:27.047" end="00:27.239">like</span> <span begin="00:27.239" end="00:27.460">a</span> <span begin="00:27.460" end="00:27.675">Rap</span> <span begin="00:27.888" end="00:28.132">God</span> <span begin="00:28.306" end="00:28.532">Rap</span> <span begin="00:28.706" end="00:28.927">God</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">开始感觉自己俨然是说唱天神</span></p><p begin="00:29.180" end="00:32.184" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:29.180" end="00:29.351">All</span> <span begin="00:29.351" end="00:29.552">my</span> <span begin="00:29.552" end="00:29.752">peo</span><span begin="00:29.752" end="00:29.955">ple</span> <span begin="00:29.955" end="00:30.080">from</span> <span begin="00:30.080" end="00:30.192">the</span> <span begin="00:30.192" end="00:30.402">front</span> <span begin="00:30.402" end="00:30.597">to</span> <span begin="00:30.597" end="00:30.781">the</span> <span begin="00:30.781" end="00:31.049">back</span> <span begin="00:31.200" end="00:31.412">nod</span> <span begin="00:31.600" end="00:31.754">back</span> <span begin="00:31.964" end="00:32.184">nod</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">跟随我的信众 从前至后 无不点头称是</span></p><p begin="00:32.184" end="00:35.433" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:32.184" end="00:32.371">Now</span> <span begin="00:32.371" end="00:32.560">who</span> <span begin="00:32.560" end="00:32.743">thinks</span> <span begin="00:32.743" end="00:32.897">their</span> <span begin="00:32.897" end="00:33.108">arms</span> <span begin="00:33.108" end="00:33.402">are</span> <span begin="00:33.402" end="00:33.490">long</span> <span begin="00:33.490" end="00:33.609">e</span><span begin="00:33.609" end="00:33.799">nough</span> <span begin="00:33.799" end="00:34.075">to</span> <span begin="00:34.075" end="00:34.286">slap</span> <span begin="00:34.416" end="00:34.666">box</span> <span begin="00:34.780" end="00:35.007">slap</span> <span begin="00:35.193" end="00:35.433">box</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在 谁觉得自己手臂够长 能跟我对打掌掴拳击？</span></p><p begin="00:35.433" end="00:37.758" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:35.433" end="00:35.650">They</span> <span begin="00:35.650" end="00:35.705">said</span> <span begin="00:35.705" end="00:35.844">I</span> <span begin="00:35.844" end="00:36.098">rap</span> <span begin="00:36.098" end="00:36.191">like</span> <span begin="00:36.191" end="00:36.272">a</span> <span begin="00:36.272" end="00:36.504">ro</span><span begin="00:36.504" end="00:36.668">bot</span> <span begin="00:36.668" end="00:36.866">so</span> <span begin="00:36.866" end="00:37.041">call</span> <span begin="00:37.041" end="00:37.282">me</span> <span begin="00:37.282" end="00:37.654">rap</span><span begin="00:37.654" end="00:37.758">-bot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">人们说我饶舌时像是机器人 所以请叫我饶舌机</span></p><p begin="00:37.853" end="00:40.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:37.853" end="00:38.070">But</span> <span begin="00:38.070" end="00:38.160">for</span> <span begin="00:38.160" end="00:38.280">me</span> <span begin="00:38.280" end="00:38.340">to</span> <span begin="00:38.340" end="00:38.550">rap</span> <span begin="00:38.550" end="00:38.670">like</span> <span begin="00:38.670" end="00:38.730">a</span> <span begin="00:38.730" end="00:38.909">com</span><span begin="00:38.909" end="00:39.061">pu</span><span begin="00:39.061" end="00:39.210">ter</span> <span begin="00:39.210" end="00:39.270">it</span> <span begin="00:39.270" end="00:39.390">must</span> <span begin="00:39.390" end="00:39.510">be</span> <span begin="00:39.510" end="00:39.600">in</span> <span begin="00:39.600" end="00:39.710">my</span> <span begin="00:39.710" end="00:40.200">genes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对我来说 像电脑一样饶舌 必是我基因所定</span></p><p begin="00:40.290" end="00:41.952" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:40.290" end="00:40.380">I</span> <span begin="00:40.380" end="00:40.408">got</span> <span begin="00:40.408" end="00:40.590">a</span> <span begin="00:40.590" end="00:40.804">lap</span><span begin="00:40.804" end="00:40.930">top</span> <span begin="00:41.062" end="00:41.128">in</span> <span begin="00:41.128" end="00:41.379">my</span> <span begin="00:41.379" end="00:41.634">back</span> <span begin="00:41.634" end="00:41.822">po</span><span begin="00:41.822" end="00:41.952">cket</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我仔裤后袋中 装着一台笔记本电脑</span></p><p begin="00:41.952" end="00:43.590" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:41.952" end="00:42.150">My</span> <span begin="00:42.150" end="00:42.320">pen'll</span> <span begin="00:42.320" end="00:42.464">go</span> <span begin="00:42.464" end="00:42.614">off</span> <span begin="00:42.614" end="00:42.787">when</span> <span begin="00:42.787" end="00:42.945">I</span> <span begin="00:42.945" end="00:43.206">half</span><span begin="00:43.206" end="00:43.400">-cock</span> <span begin="00:43.400" end="00:43.590">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我半上膛的笔蓄势待发 随时开火</span></p><p begin="00:43.650" end="00:45.116" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span beg